name: AngelDice.GitHub.io
tagline: Be an angel and gamble up to the moon.
body:
### So you were Fed up with provably UNFAIR dice sites where they scam you off with ever promising 0.1 house edge.
### Well tell them to go Fuck themselves because we are darn tired of their unpromising promises.
### Let's have fun with moneypot's bankroll and be true thugs.
### Roll. Earn. Thuglife. Be an Angel.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
